'From Squeak2.6 of 13 October 1999 [latest update: #1733] on 27 December 1999 at 3:31:09 pm'!"Change Set:		CompressionPostFix-arDate:			27 December 1999Author:			Andreas RaabA fix for a compression fix in the last change set, e.g., a post-fix ;-)" !!InflateStream methodsFor: 'private' stamp: 'ar 12/27/1999 15:25'!pastEndRead	"A client has attempted to read beyond the read limit.	Check in what state we currently are and perform	the appropriate action"	| blockType |	state = StateNoMoreData ifTrue:[^nil]. "Get out early if possible"	"Check if we can move decoded data to front"	self moveContentsToFront.	"Check if we can fetch more source data"	self moveSourceToFront.	state = StateNewBlock ifTrue:[state _ self getNextBlock].	blockType _ state bitShift: -1.	self perform: (BlockTypes at: blockType+1).	^self next! !